    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299270/extras/001fc8292ad3cf3921a1733d0bca3301.poster.avif?t=1636099767\" width=384 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299270/extras/001fc8292ad3cf3921a1733d0bca3301.webm?t=1636099767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>深入王国的黑暗之地。化身哥特风恐怖动作角色扮演游戏《赤痕》中的碎片人米莉雅姆等独特的君主，获得相应的强大特性。骑上巨大的甲虫，布设陷阱；骑上诡异的不死生物，召唤障碍，阻止贪婪生物的侵袭；或者骑上《赤痕》神秘的恶魔生物加麦基，发动强大的冲刺攻击。玩家将获得前所未有的恐怖体验！<br><br>我们将在正式发售之后，延续《王国：两位君主》的探索、发现和策略元素，加入更多主题鲜明的设定。各个设定风格迥异，不仅可以通过不同的方式治理，还能看到令人惊叹的风景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299270/extras/ad48ad029a03cd644329a8115756170d.poster.avif?t=1636099767\" width=384 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299270/extras/ad48ad029a03cd644329a8115756170d.webm?t=1636099767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
